<TITLE>SAVIN &lt;SVB> IN PACT WITH SUN CHEMICAL &lt;SNLA></TITLE>
<DATELINE>    STAMFORD, Conn., March 3 - </DATELINE><BODY>Savin Corp said it has reached
an agreement for Sun Chemical Corp to study the potential of
Savin infrared technology for possible use in classified U.S.
military applications.
